<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>HEAVENLY LADDER</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Jakob Guol pha leh a Lei sang kha,
 Ka Pathien, ka Bangkim Nang na hi;
 Thihna luipi kinawk chung ahin,
 Aw, van Lei pha, hung kidawh kit in!

[V2]
 Hung kidawh in, Jordan lui achun,
 Thavai lo a ka hung lem kaih na'n;
 Aw, van Zingsawl ei hung pui in la,
 Thihna luipi lien chung ahin.

[V3]
 2. Lalpa, van lei a Na kidawh leh,
 Na cha gal lau a vakvaite hi;
 Muong leh dam in Na van Kanaan chu,
 Hung lem kai thei phet ding ka hiu hi.

[V4]
 3. Ginna Lei, Pielgal kaihna lo chuh,
 Lei dang bangmah a um hielpuoi maw!
 Zeziek chun aw, Palai Lal Krista,
 Gin chawmte lung leh van lei zawm ta'n.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>10</hymn_number>
</song>